snippet.title: Mario Takes a Three - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
MTA3 was an unofficial SMB3 based level contest held on June of 2019. This is a compilation of levels from the said contest. We are NOT affiliated with Nintendo, and this game is 100% free. If you like what you're
seeing here, please go support Nintendo.

https://mfgg.net/index.php?act=resdb&param=02&c=2&id=36312

This trailer was originally only released on Twitter back in December 2019, it's now uploaded on YouTube for preservation purposes.
